commitResults.messageBody:
Change help button to open UserGuide (UG) directly on browser instead of
having to copy UG URL, opening browser, then pasting it inside for user
convenience.
Also add optional topic to HelpCommand (e.g. `help add`) to allow user
to directly search for specific help for a particular command.
Maintains window with URL if browswer cannot be opened.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add anchors for features implemented in v1.3
commitResults.messageBody:
Add anchors for Help command for features implemented in v1.3.
Features include: relation, transaction, find t/, find a/, clear and
exit so that users can find help easily for new commands.

Minor changes in UserGuide to reflect updates.

Allows users to archive contacts to view active list of contacts. Users
can also view archive list and choose to unarchive contacts from the
archive list.

Move 'list' parsing logic from AddressBookParser to ListCommandParser
to follow SLAP. Support 'list', 'list active' and 'list archive'
commands.
